data.description: NO SHOWINGS AT THIS TIME Welcome to a piece of history in the heart of Bountiful, built in 1910. Step in a large entryway. lovely living/sitting room, a touch of old world charm.  Kitchen is retro style with island and room for your dining room table. Upstairs features 2 beds and a bathroom with a bonus room that can function as an office or playroom for the kids.  Downstairs offers a mother-in-law apartment with a full kitchen. There is work in progress. The garage is currently used for storage.
